1. An email with your order no. on info@shopsvirtually.com Or Click Here
2. Call with your return request & order no. on +255688301818 3. WhatsApp your return request with order no. on +255688301818 Or Click Here Your item must be in its original unused condition to be returned. Merchandise that has been worn, used or altered will not be accepted for return or exchange. Please note damage does not include any issue with the product pertaining to the style/design of the product. Bleeding and rubbing of vegetable dyes (especially the Indigo dye) is not a defect. Similarly, minor stitching issues in Quilts may occur even after rigorous quality checks. This may happen during the quilts undergoing packing process & will not be considered as a defect.
Please note that minor variations in color (up to 10%) may be seen due to different monitors and will not be treated as not as per description. Return Charges
1. All returns requested for other than any quality defect like not being as per your taste/likes will levy a return shipping charge of TSH10,000- (inclusive VAT) per product ( weight up to 1.5 KG).
2. In the case of quilts & comforters the Return Shipping Charges will be TSH 10,000- (inclusive VAT) for every single bed quilt & 10,000/- (inclusive vat) for every double bed quilt Merchandise that has been worn, used, or altered will not be accepted for return or exchange.
Exchanges If your item is in like-new condition, you may exchange it for a different one. You will not be subject to a restocking fee in this case, but you still will have to pay return shipping.
Sending the product back
Once we receive your exchange request, we will organize a Reverse Pickup. When the product is received and approved by our quality team, we will issue a refund equal to the amount of your purchase only. Please note the shipping fee is non-refundable. This process can take anything between 7 to 14 days. In case, our courier partner does not provide Reverse Pickup from your location, you will need to ship it back to us. Kindly send the product back to us within 7 days of receiving it.
NO RETURN ON SALE ITEMS -
Products purchased by you during our sale will not be liable for any return/refund.
